            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>pro <expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>ute</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Catul<lb break="no" n="5"/>linus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>artiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>cond</abbr><ex>uctor</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>prat</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Fur</abbr><ex>iani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lustr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Nert</abbr><ex cert="low">i</ex></expan> Cele<lb break="no" n="10"/>rini <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rimi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Oct</abbr><ex>obribus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Anton</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> II et Geta </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>are</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Basis. Zeile 13/14 befinden sich auf der crepido auf verschiedenen Teilen des Fußprofils. Zeile 2 klein im Zeilenzwischenraum 1/3 stehend. Zeile 3: AV-Ligatur; Zeile 13: MP-, AV-Ligatur; A klein am Zeilenende z.T. unter Querhaste des T stehend. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buschstaben. Zeile 9: Nert(i) oder Nert(oni). (B): kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
